Class CellTransferable

java.lang.Object
  csheets.ui.sheet.CellTransferable
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.datatransfer.ClipboardOwner, java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable
public class CellTransferable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.awt.datatransfer.ClipboardOwner

A transferable for transferring a range of cells. Cells are transferred either as objects locally within the Java VM, or exported as strings.

Author:
Einar Pehrson
